Installation guide: To use this website, you must first install XAMPP, activate MySQL database and Apache Web Server using the graphical manager or the terminal. Then open phpMyAdmin and export the file campus_booking.sql into it. Lastly you need to run the file server.js on node.js and got to the Login page: http://localhost:3000/login_page.html

User guide: If you know the password you can login directly. Otherwise, you will need to create an account student and faculty member are similar in function, since they can book reservations and cancel them. On the other hand, Ressource manager approve the reservation bookings. After registration and loging in, you will be able to see a sidebar with all the available choices. before reserving or booking a room or anything else, you should first head to ressource List to check all the available ressources especially the ID of the ressource, because you will be needing it for later to logout, you should go to the profile page.
